extendedInfo.description: Everyone knows that choosing a tattoo can be a challenging. You should always pick a design that you will be comfortable with, ideally it will be a permanent fixture. See grate collection of the latest trends 2010, 2011, 2012, tattoo ideas including tribal, Celtic, cross, memorial, Japanese, Kanji, and many more! Tattoos can be wonderful things that allow you as an individual to express you spiritually, your status, youâre commitment to a loved one or just to show people that you like to defy convention. Some popular can include a dragon, which may represent courage. Tattoos help in expressing your individuality to the fullest and if you are that kind of a person who wants to stand out in the crowd, tribal patterns are the best option for you. The best place to get a tribal design inked is the lower back for woman and the shoulder blade for men. Tribal help in giving a traditional plus modern look as in the earlier times they were drawn to mark the passage to new responsibilities like adulthood. Find out Asian, Lotus, sun and moon, alien, wings, hearts and pinup tattoos. Rib tat give a lot of freedom to the bearer to choose a large enough design, for there is ample space around ribs to serve as a canvas. Chest tats are exciting and look highly sexy. Your chest tat should be unique and it should represent you. Tattoos, of any kind, cannot be worn by everyone. Face tats cover a part of the face or the neck or the head or all of them together but mostly the initial most option is preferred. Check out cool tips also for arm, hip, wrist, spine, forearm, sleeves, ankle and foot. The three most common tips that girls generally like and get are roses, butterflies, fantasy and fairies. A butterfly, symbolizes the birth of a baby or re-birth. Talking about feminine tattoos, women like to sport designs that find consonance with their nature. These tat exhibit softness, grace, beauty, sweetness and various other qualities that are associated with women. The most common tips that they like are flowers, birds, fishes and cute cartoon characters. The world of feminine tats is quite colorful and interesting just like the women. Enjoy very realistic 3D, stars, abstract symbol, zodiac and lettering. Tattoos are a huge rage among men. Call them art or describe them as an inspiration they are sensational. They also are an extension of their personality. All that you have to do is pick something that you relate to and are fond of. The rest will be executed by the tattoo artist. Browse through our Gothic tattoos which include fairies, angel, and cross themed. Also you will find Jesus, Devil and death tats. Lion and tiger are very popular subjects. The eagle has many positive meanings and the eagle has been used in symbolism for centuries. If youâre looking for inspiration for your next picture on your body or just feel like checking out some great designs youâve come to the right place!P.S.
